snippet.title: 1000 MOTICHOOR LADDU | Soft Laddu Recipe Cooking in Village | Boondi Laddu Making | Sweet Recipe
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 1000 Motichoor Laddu using crushed pearls. Normally, laddu is made with Boondi, but Motichoor laddu is made using smashed Boondi. That is why Moticoor Laddu is special and so soft.

The taste is Yummy!

snippet.title: All India Rank | Official Trailer | Varun Grover | Sriram Raghavan | In Theatres 23rd Feb 2024
snippet.description:
Sriram Raghavan presents Masaan & Sacred Games writer Varun Grover's directorial debut ALL INDIA RANK. 

Releasing in theatres all over India on 23rd Feb 2024. 

A coming-of-age comedy-drama set in the late 90s - 17-year-old Lucknow boy Vivek Singh struggles with the ambitions & mediocrity of his parents while prepping for India‚Äôs toughest under-grad exam in an IIT coaching in Kota. A story of possible dreams and impossible competition.

Written & Directed By: Varun Grover

Produced By: Sanjay Routray and Sarita Patil

Une jaane saara shehar

Mere kamb jawe paer

Re main khaa ke marr jau, chhora lagge mane zehar re‚Ä¶

Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humour of the show. snippet.title: PM Modi And CM Naveen Meet At Sambalpur, IIM Campus | PM Modi Odisha Visit | PM Modi In Sambalpur
snippet.description:
PM Modi And CM Naveen Meet At Sambalpur, IIM Campus | PM Modi Odisha Visit | PM Modi In Sambalpur
The Prime Minister inaugurated the permanent IIM Sambalpur campus in the presence of Odisha Governor Raghubar Das, Chief Minister Naveen Patnaik, Union Ministers Dharmendra Pradhan, Ashwini Vaishnaw and other BJP leaders.  Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Saturday inaugurated the permanent campus of the Indian Institute of Management (IIM), Sambalpur. Modi was accorded a grand welcome at Jharsuguda airport upon his arrival on one-day visit to Odisha.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. ----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: How much 'Titanium' is Samsung *actually* using? - NO SECRETS HERE!
snippet.description:
Lets take apart the new Samsung S24 Ultra! Grab one of my teardown skins for your own phone HERE: https://www.dbrand.com/teardown

HUGE thanks to Moxtec for letting me borrow their XRF Scanner. If you ever want to build a rover to analyze other planets - check them out: https://www.moxtek.com/ and massive thanks to @NFTI for letting me borrow his forge so we can separate the plastic, aluminum, and Titanium of the Galaxy S24 Ultra.

I'm a big fan of Titanium smartphones, its a super cool metal. And I'm glad to see that both Samsung, and Apple are using the real stuff. Even if it is different grades of the Titanium material.

Samsung is using Grade 2 Titanium, and Apple is using Grade 5 Titanium.

snippet.title: Khuda ki Inayat Hai | Sun Soniye Sun Dildar | Heart Touching Love Story | Sad Song | Maahi Queen
snippet.description:
Presenting the most heart touching love story of 2024, Khuda Ki Inayat Hai, featuring Maahi Queen and Aryan. Watch how their love transcends all barriers and challenges in this emotional saga. The song is sung by Tarun Panchal and Renuka Panwar, composed by TR Music and written by Pradeep Sonu. The video is directed by Arvind Chauhan and produced by Jeetu Bhai. Don‚Äôt forget to like, share and subscribe to our channel for more amazing videos.

Producer: Jeetu Bhai

üîó Original Song Link: Sun Soniyo Sun Dildar

üìñ Lyrics:

Sun Soniye Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar‚Ä¶

Khuda Ki Inayat Hai,
Hamme Jo Milaya Hia,
Diya Pyaar Wala,
Ye Dil Mein Jalaya Hai..
 
Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar‚Ä¶

Tu Hi Khuda Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar,
Tu Hi Khuda
Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar..
Lagta Hai Darr Tu Chhod Na Jaaye,
Jaaye To Jaan Sang Le Jaaye..

Dil Ki Hai Dhadkan,
Aakhon Ka Deedar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada Tujhe,
Karte Hai Pyaar..

Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar‚Ä¶

Khuda Ki Inayat Hai,
Hamme Jo Milaya Hia,
Diya Pyaar Wala,
Ye Dil Mein Jalaya Hai..

Hai Tu saanso Mein ,
Aakhon Mein Mere Yaar,
Khud Se Jyada,
Tujhe Karti Hoon Pyaar‚Ä¶

Tu Hi Khuda Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar..

Apna Sabse Juda Hum Banayenge,
Pyaari Si Khushiyan Chunke,
Duniya Se Laayenge..

Itna To Kar Mujhpe Aitbaar,
Rabb Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karte Hai Pyaar,
Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar, 
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar..

Teri Parchai Se Durr Kaise Jaaungi,
Tujhme Basi Hoon Main,
Tujhme Kho Jaaungi..

Meri Palkon Pe Hai Tera Izhaar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar‚Ä¶

Some strange people come inside the Gokuldham society and demand money for the festivals. Daya, Komal, and Babita are buying vegetables and encounter them on the way. They start asking each and every one a large sum of money as donations. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 435
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Wrath of Salaar | Music By Ravi Basrur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Witness the vengeance, feel the power - Wrath of Salaar 

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the First Single of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films.
 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.
